NAME
	query_wizard - test if a player is a wizard

SYNOPSIS
	int query_wizard(object arg)

DESCRIPTION
	Check if 'arg' is a wizard player object

RETURN VALUE
	Returns 1 if 'arg' is a wizard player object, 0 otherwise.

EXAMPLES
	if (query_wizard(this_player()) {
		write("You may pass.\n");
	}

SEE ALSO
	afun/query_admin, afun/query_mortal, afun/query_user_type
